ght: 30px; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0;">Welcome back to Wall Power.=
 I=E2=80=99m <b>Marion Maneker</b>. <br/><br/>What would you do if you were=
 the curator of a major museum in the hinterlands and you picked up the pho=
ne one day to learn that a once-famous but now reclusive artist had died an=
d bequeathed her <i>entire estate</i> to your museum? <b>Cathleen Chaffee</=
b>, Buffalo AKG=E2=80=99s chief curator, swiftly planned a retrospective of=
 the artist=E2=80=99s career=E2=80=94better to fund the arduous work of cat=
aloging the bequest with an achievable goal. Tonight, we=E2=80=99re going t=
o talk about that artist, <b>Marisol</b>, and the retrospective Chaffee cre=
ated. <br/></p>
